main event: Two amber colored objects were observed extending and descending on a vertical plane over Griffithville, Arkansas.
interesting points: The objects exhibited zig-zag movements,The objects appeared to turn on and off like a light,The duration of the observation was between 5 to 15 minutes,The investigation concluded the sighting was likely caused by astronomical phenomena,No physical evidence was found to support the sighting.
witness description: Civilian observer with an interest in aerial phenomena
